        "created_at": "2020-11-06T20:14:48.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>It\u2019s exceptional! It\u2019s a finer-boned, more elegant vintage for him than 2015\u2014pretty much as you would expect. Notes will be coming out in TWA in due course, but I\u2019m somewhat wrapped up in 2019 Burgundy reviews for the moment to write them up in full.</p>\n<p>In the meantime, here is a video I did of C\u00e9dric talking about La Bolor\u00e9e and Les Ursules\u2026</p>\n<p>          <iframe src=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CG7URyHiCgU/embed\" width=\"640\" height=\"1235\" frameborder=\"0\" seamless=\"seamless\" sandbox=\"allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-presentation\"></iframe>\n</p>",
